</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[212,1171,1595,1691]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1733">
<collectingRegion box="[212,318,1635,1659]" country="Russia" name="Primorskiy" pageId="2" pageNumber="1733">Maritime</collectingRegion>
transport or unintentional introduction/established (
<bibRefCitation author="Daguin C &amp; Borsa P" pageId="2" pageNumber="1733" pagination="389 - 397" refId="ref9849" refString="Daguin C, Borsa P. 2000. Genetic relationships of Mytilus galloprovincialis Lmk. populations worldwide: evidence from nuclear-DNA markers. In: Crame A, Harper E, Taylor J, editors. Bivalve systematics and evolution, Vol. 177. London: Geological Society of London Special Publications; p. 389 - 397." type="book chapter" year="2000">Daguin and Borsa 2000</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Tarifeno E &amp; Galleguillos R &amp; Rivera A &amp; Arriagada D &amp; Ferrada S &amp; Aguirre CB &amp; Seguel M" box="[355,580,1667,1691]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1733" pagination="167 - 172" refId="ref13867" refString="Tarifeno E, Galleguillos R, Llanos- Rivera A, Arriagada D, Ferrada S, Canales- Aguirre CB, Seguel M. 2012. Erroneous identification of the mussel, Mytilus galloprovincialis (Lamarck 1819) as the species Mytilus chilensis (Hupe, 1854) in the Bay of Concepcion, Chile. Gayana. 76: 167 - 172." type="journal article" year="2012">Tarifeño et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
